# @DISPLAY_NAME@ -- AI Development Notes (index)

**Load topic files on demand -- do not read this entire index repeatedly.**

## Quick rules

- Branding: always lowercase `@DISPLAY_NAME@`
- Text: ASCII-only in docs, logs, help, and code comments
- Agents work in session clones, NOT in Sync: Grok -> `~/.grok/worktrees/mini-projects-@PROJECT_NAME@/<session-id>/`; Claude Code -> `~/.claude/worktrees/mini-projects-@PROJECT_NAME@/<session-id>/`; CLI runs from `@SYNC_REPO@`
- Claude Code: NEVER edit files under `@SYNC_REPO@` -- use absolute paths to your session clone only
- New Grok session: run `scripts/init_grok_session.sh`; new Claude Code session: run `scripts/init_claude_session.sh` (see `agentstartstack/ai-guidance/workflow.md`)
- After changes: commit in session clone; human runs `nut` then `git push origin main` (or `nutup`). NEVER `git push origin` from agents (see `agentstartstack/ai-guidance/nut.md`)

